727225f-a.text:
Liberty Ave., north side, between 105th and 106th Street, showing the A. Van Sicklen house, erected about 1886 or 1887. Eugene L. Armbruster states this house has been moved from the above location. However, he does not state to what location.
August 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster.
